last_episode_to_air.name: Defying Gravity
last_episode_to_air.overview: Hip-hop illusionist Jibrizy defies gravity with a simple deck of playing cards in Chicago, Scott Xavier reads minds on the Jersey Shore, Justin Flom conjures a flower out of thin air in the Nevada desert and much more.

name: Magic Caught on Camera
overview: Magicians across the US and around the world take to the streets to perform mind-blowing illusions. From city to city they amaze and bewilder passersby with never-before-seen card tricks, hypnosis, sleight of hand, levitation, vanishing acts and more!
